---
title: Baked Squash and Shrimp Ravioli Al Forno with Mozzarella and Veggies
description: A meal as comforting as it is delicious. Smooth butternut squash-filled ravioli is baked with roasted zucchini and spinach in a hearty tomato sauce and topped with shrimp and stretchy mozzarella for the ultimate cheese pull.
